   "source": [
    "## Lens Formula\n",
    "\n",
    "$$ \\large \\frac{1}{\\text{O}} + \\frac{1}{\\text{I}} = \\frac{1}{\\text{F}}$$\n",
    "\n",
    "\n",
    "### Focal Lengh (F)\n",
    "\n",
    "(+): Convergent\n",
    "\n",
    "(-): Divergent"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "30d8c4f0",
